1. Molim te za *pomoć* oko računara. (Please help me with the computer.)
2. Želim da *pomognem* svojoj sestri oko pripreme večere. (I want to help my sister with preparing dinner.)
3. Policija je došla da pruži *pomoć* nakon saobraćajne nesreće. (The police came to provide assistance after a car accident.)
4. Ova organizacija pruža *pomoć* siromašnim porodicama. (This organization provides assistance to poor families.)
5. Ako nešto trebaš, samo mi reci - uvek sam tu da ti *pomognem*. (If you need anything, just tell me - I'm always here to help you.)
6. *Pomoćnik* ministra je objasnio novu politiku. (The minister's assistant explained the new policy.)
7. Ona je *pomogla* svom prijatelju da pronađe posao. (She helped her friend find a job.)
8. Kada sam bio bolestan, moja majka mi je pružila mnogo *pomoći*. (When I was sick, my mother provided me with a lot of help.)
9. Naša organizacija je osnovana da pruži *pomoć* ženama žrtvama nasilja. (Our organization was founded to provide assistance to women who are victims of violence.)
10. Novi zakon će omogućiti veću *pomoć* poljoprivrednicima. (The new law will enable greater assistance to farmers.)